Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello! This video is a special release provided to all of you by Shounen Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you watch this video, please brighten the room and don't sit to close to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:41.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,16 suspects
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Caviar, fois gras, oysters! I can't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Low calorie foods, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dreary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko, I wonder if I can eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, this food isn't just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector Shiratori, these are called hors d'oeuvres, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you don't care for the\NFrench cuisine we're having this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I made these appetizers especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, they look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They really do look delicious, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? A glass of champagne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, my, Inspector{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-dono{\r}, that's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the wrong glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one is for champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make every little thing an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't drink enough with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:02:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't drink this without stopping like you do normal liquor. This one is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bossy woman, mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The air is so fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad we came, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, seems we really chose a perfect time to come visit Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! This is the first time I've been to Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Considering your family, Sonoko, I expected you would have a villa in Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we don't have one in Karuizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have villas in Hawaii, Nice, Monaco and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:44.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One day in the fall,\NInspector Shiratori invited his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:47.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To a party to celebrate the completion of his villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:54.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The highlight of the party was\NInspector Shiratori's collection of expensive wines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Inspector Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the wine you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall I show everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stairs are steep, so please be carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the restrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The women's on the right,\Nand the men's on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And over here we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed. Is this all the wine cellar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's as big as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your house has a wine cellar too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s parents run a liquor store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please patronize Kojima Liquors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a wine rack that I had specially made from real oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is where I keep my most precious wines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, this is a 1979 Château Margaux.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1985 Château Lafite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1992 Le Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is today's selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A 1961 Château Latour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think I just saw something floating in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, has it gone bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is called the sediment.\NIt's formed when the wine ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only mature wines have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the {sedimentation}precipitation process {is disrupted}fails, sometimes even half of the wine is ruined and thrown away.{the wine may deteriorate and has to be thrown away.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Inspector Shiratori, is that wine really that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's completely different than a cheaper one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell right away when you taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Why is the next bottle section empty?}Hey, the next slot is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There used to be a bottle of 1989 Sassicaia here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister and her husband drank it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, shall we return to the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji, look, the floor in this section is made of marble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God, it must've been terribly expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone has their own hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, everyone,\NI'm going to prepare the main dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please relax for about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? What's with the big sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, it's just that\NInspector Shiratori has so much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, this is the wealth of\NShiratori's family, not Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're a man,\Ndon't worry about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about that case the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's because I'm a man that I have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder what the other rooms here are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, let's go explore for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's do it. It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go for a walk around the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but I'm not familiar with the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let me show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you've been here before?{DCTP: Eh? You know the area?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Shin'ichi's parents brought me here once{before}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah yeah, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm okay,{Oh, go without me.} I have something else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Something to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just something.{Nothing special.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass too, but the four of you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this street is called the "Whispering Path".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the "Whispering Path"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji, whisper something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Bring your ear closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,AN IDIOT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got you, got you!{DCTP: You fell for it, you fell for it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kyu-Karuizawa Christian Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, a wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you just imagining doing that with Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?{Did you imagine yourself and Kudo-kun in their place just now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI wasn't imagining anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Then what was with that dreamy expression on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about you, Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWe don't do that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what kind of thing you don't do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who is this "we"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kumoba Pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi and I rode our bikes here from their riverside villa.{from his house to this shore.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, right? It seems so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why, it's only been two or three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:18.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something get in your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, let's walk a bit farther in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an island called the "Water Bird Island" this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ah, }A swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.47,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.30,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Love - 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can we use our legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:26.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course not, this isn't soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:32.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait, Shinichi! Where are we going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just follow me and you'll know{find out}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:35.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's so quiet{calm} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that they left without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, that Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, sorry for the wait!{DCTP: Sorry to have kept you waiting, everyone.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's main dish is ready.{The main dish for today is ready.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure does! What kind of dish is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roast lamb shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ninzaburo-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you make this too{Did you cook that yourself}, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, cooking is another hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not bad! You'd make a great son-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:44.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eeek!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm off to get our wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ah, }Welcome back, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you two did come back without us.{DCTP: So, you two did return already.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but Heiji suddenly said he wanted to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing{in particular}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Ran, is it okay to leave him like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. He's probably just tired from driving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's terrible! My Château Latour...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has been smashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, how much was this wine worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get this kind of wine now\Nwould probably cost several million.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Several million!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's either slipped from\Nsomeone's hand when they took it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or it was broken by someone on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, that's completely obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who could have done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is, there isn't much chance that it was an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Common sense would say, the suspect is someone here{one of us}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's discuss it in\Nthe living room instead of down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, I'll come back and clean it up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-We're not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, we should get going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What we know now is that after our visit to the wine cellar,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And before Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s second trip down there{went down there a second time},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the time in which this case must have occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Case"? Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, did anyone go down to\Nthe cellar during this period of time?{DCTP: Say, during that time, did anyone go into the wine cellar?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were exploring inside the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we went into the wine cellar too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we never touched that bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that in your drunken stupor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't wander into the wine cellar after going to the restroom and break the wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! How could I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I can't remember anything other than going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, doesn't that make you the most likely suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, calm down.\NLots of people went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For example, I also went...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you have broken my Latour out of jealousy, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we really rule out the possibility that you broke it yourself?{And can we be sure that you didn't break it yourself?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, you two.{Stop it, both of you!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, you've been quiet for a while. That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there was someone who for some reason left here looking serious and holding a handbag.{Except for one person who went out with a bag with a serious look.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, where could that thing have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, someone picked it up and ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, only you would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something from me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} dropped a grape in the wine cellar,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it rolled underneath a wine rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we just looked before and it had vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone must have picked it up and thrown it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With this... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bottle is new!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odd{Strange}, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing what that little girl said, I finally understood it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person here capable of doing this is her.{She is the only person who could've done this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the solution to this case?{You've solved the case?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the culprit who broke that wine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is annoying, hurry and tell us{tell us already}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry Kudo. Ah, no, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Go ahead and tell us, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, the culprit is a dormouse that snuck into the villa.{In fact, the culprit is a dormouse who accidentally sneaked into this villa.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dormouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dormouse? You mean those little guys that look like mice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dormouse that snuck into the villa\Nwas drawn by the sweet aroma{attracted by the smells from the wine cellar} of the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it went downstairs to the door of the wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, at the same time, Mitsuhiko and the others were checking out the wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it got into the wine cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! It was the dormouse who ate the grape that Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} dropped!{DCTP: That's it! The dormouse must have eaten the grape that Genta-kun dropped.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later, after the three of them left, it was startled when Uncle came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dormouse climbed up the special wine rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hid inside the empty wine slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle didn't notice this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he mistakenly put the wine in the empty slot that the dormouse had gone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, after Uncle left, the dormouse pushed the wine bottle out and it smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the evidence is...{As for evidence,}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look{ at this}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:41.62,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Japanese Dormouse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it behind the wine rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already halfway into its winter sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will you do now, Dad?\NYou'll have to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think that will be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because that wine was fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, the real one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is my Château Latour!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?{What does it mean?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, you don't have to pretend anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I've been found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing is, not long ago at a family party,\Nwe finished a bottle of the same wine.{The fact is that we recently finished a bottle of the same wine at a family party}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I had this bright idea, and I switched the label with a cheap Latour and brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just think of it as a cute prank by a young girl!{Consider this a little girlish prank!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my{Come on}, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, considering the result, it's good you did it.{Well, thanks to you, everything worked out.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, it was because\Nof you that the wine was saved.{Exactly! Thanks to you, the wine bottle was not damaged.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, shall we all make a toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.44,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thus the case was over{solved}, and the party became happy once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Other than Uncle, who was forbidden to drink by Auntie, and...{Everyone, except Uncle, who was forbidden to drink by Auntie...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hattori Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is your sock rolled up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there some reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this? This is the latest{DCTP: newest} style in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You broke the wine, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under the rolled up part of your sock,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is a wine stain from when the bottle broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's solid evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you did know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I went to the restroom, I wanted to look at the expensive wine once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I went to the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in the same place as before\Nand it was sticking out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's strange..." I thought,\Nand as I was pulling it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dim-witted. It was the worst blunder in Hattori Heiji's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo, I wanted to own up right away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} also noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she said, "This is a perfect way to restrict my husband's drinking, work with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have been written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:40.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,I\NDID\NIT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it, that so-called stupid honesty is kind of a plus for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is just looking out for Uncle's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't say anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed, I owe you yet another favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:22:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just returning your favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:07.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Idiot, because of you I was able to feel again what I haven't felt for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I won't say it even if you pry my mouth open.
